    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person\u2014it\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, and it shows in every single detail. It\u2019s super clean, smells brand new, and drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s in truly flawless shape, this is the one for you. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself, you're going to love it!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
