    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E46 M3, showcasing the pinnacle of atmospheric S54 engineering. This example features a meticulously maintained 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox. Performance is anchored by a factory-spec M-variable limited-slip differential and a reinforced rear subframe, addressing the chassis's known structural stress points. The VANOS system has been fully overhauled with Beisan components, and rod bearings were serviced preventatively. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the paint meter readings are consistent throughout, confirming a collision-free history. This is a turn-key collector piece with zero deferred maintenance, optimized for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
