      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m a little heartbroken to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolute mint condition\u2014I've babied it since day one and it still looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. No scratches, no dings, and the interior is just flawless. It drives like a total dream! If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the brand new price tag, you\u2019ve found it. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 43500.0,
